  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >THE ROGUELIKE WITH NO PLAYER CHARACTER</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >RAM is a top-down roguelike shooter with a defining twist: you don’t have a body. You play as a rogue AI, jumping between enemy robots to survive. Turn your enemies into your weapons and fight your way through a post-apocalyptic world run by quirky robots.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BODY-SWAPPING COMBAT</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every enemy is a potential host. Switch control at a moment’s notice between unique enemy types, each with a distinct moveset and playstyle, and their own arsenal of upgrades to unlock.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >          <br>          <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256450/extras/0c58997780c787e564b5b7c5c489708d.poster.avif?t=1757960780\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256450/extras/0c58997780c787e564b5b7c5c489708d.webm?t=1757960780\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256450/extras/0c58997780c787e564b5b7c5c489708d.mp4?t=1757960780\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <br>APOCALYPSE COMES TO THE POST-APOCALYPSE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Digital pets. Student projects. Sentient memes. Within a year, they were all that remained of intelligent life. After ten, it was just the strong ones. And in 2120… one of them made you. How much longer until there’s nothing left at all?<br>Traverse the ruins of the human world across multiple procedurally-generated levels, and contend with the eccentric mechanical societies that have risen to inhabit them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >              <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256450/extras/2f4543103bc643f1f4232d099085e9ff.poster.avif?t=1757960780\" width=480 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256450/extras/2f4543103bc643f1f4232d099085e9ff.webm?t=1757960780\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256450/extras/2f4543103bc643f1f4232d099085e9ff.mp4?t=1757960780\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >STYLE IS LEGAL TENDER</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >RAM expands the style systems seen in games like Devil May Cry and Ultrakill by making style points in-run currency. Master combat techniques and execute trickshots to earn a diverse array of upgrades that modify how each host robot functions, then pit your accumulated strength against dangerous bosses with their own unique swap-related mechanics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >             <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256450/extras/61faf8fdb69fcc13f570929f27a38aae.poster.avif?t=1757960780\" width=480 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256450/extras/61faf8fdb69fcc13f570929f27a38aae.webm?t=1757960780\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256450/extras/61faf8fdb69fcc13f570929f27a38aae.mp4?t=1757960780\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256450/extras/e7a83d5c87db9521d7f5dd7e40275da0.avif?t=1757960780\" width=616 height=100 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >THE ROGUELIKE WITH NO PLAYER CHARACTER</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >RAM is a top-down roguelike shooter with a defining twist: you don’t have a body. You play as a rogue AI, jumping between enemy robots to survive. Turn your enemies into your weapons and fight your way through a post-apocalyptic world run by quirky robots.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BODY-SWAPPING COMBAT</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every enemy is a potential host. Switch control at a moment’s notice between unique enemy types, each with a distinct moveset and playstyle, and their own arsenal of upgrades to unlock.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >          <br>          <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256450/extras/0c58997780c787e564b5b7c5c489708d.poster.avif?t=1757960780\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256450/extras/0c58997780c787e564b5b7c5c489708d.webm?t=1757960780\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256450/extras/0c58997780c787e564b5b7c5c489708d.mp4?t=1757960780\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <br>APOCALYPSE COMES TO THE POST-APOCALYPSE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Digital pets. Student projects. Sentient memes. Within a year, they were all that remained of intelligent life. After ten, it was just the strong ones. And in 2120… one of them made you. How much longer until there’s nothing left at all?<br>Traverse the ruins of the human world across multiple procedurally-generated levels, and contend with the eccentric mechanical societies that have risen to inhabit them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >              <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256450/extras/2f4543103bc643f1f4232d099085e9ff.poster.avif?t=1757960780\" width=480 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256450/extras/2f4543103bc643f1f4232d099085e9ff.webm?t=1757960780\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256450/extras/2f4543103bc643f1f4232d099085e9ff.mp4?t=1757960780\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >STYLE IS LEGAL TENDER</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >RAM expands the style systems seen in games like Devil May Cry and Ultrakill by making style points in-run currency. Master combat techniques and execute trickshots to earn a diverse array of upgrades that modify how each host robot functions, then pit your accumulated strength against dangerous bosses with their own unique swap-related mechanics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >             <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256450/extras/61faf8fdb69fcc13f570929f27a38aae.poster.avif?t=1757960780\" width=480 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256450/extras/61faf8fdb69fcc13f570929f27a38aae.webm?t=1757960780\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256450/extras/61faf8fdb69fcc13f570929f27a38aae.mp4?t=1757960780\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256450/extras/e7a83d5c87db9521d7f5dd7e40275da0.avif?t=1757960780\" width=616 height=100 /></span></p>",
